{
  "chapter": "091",
  "title": "黥布列传",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "当刑而王之相",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黥布</span>，是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">六</span>地人，姓<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">英氏</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>朝时是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">布衣</span>百姓。少年时，有个相士给他看相，说：\"当受刑罚后称王。\"到壮年时，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">坐法</span>被处以<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">黥</span>刑。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>欣然笑着说：\"有人给我看相说我当受刑后称王，大概就是这样吧？\"听到的人都一同嘲笑他。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>已被判决押送到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">丽山</span>服刑，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">丽山</span>的刑徒有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数十万人</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>与刑徒的首领和<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">豪桀</span>结交，于是率领他的伙伴，逃亡到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">江</span>中做群盗。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "随项羽征战",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈胜</span>起义时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>就去见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">番君</span>，和他的部众一同<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">叛</span>离<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>朝，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">聚兵</span>达<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数千人</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">番君</span>把自己的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">女</span>儿嫁给他为妻。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">章邯</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">灭</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈胜</span>、<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">破</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕臣</span>军后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>便<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">引兵</span>向北<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">左右校</span>的军队，在清波<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">破</span>之，随即<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">引兵</span>东进。听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项梁</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">定</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">江东</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">会稽</span>，便渡江西进。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈婴</span>因为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项</span>氏世代是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国大将，于是率兵归属<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项梁</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">渡</span>过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮南</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">英布</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒲将军</span>也率兵归属<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项梁</span>。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "楚军常胜",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项梁</span>渡<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮</span>西进，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景驹</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦嘉</span>等人，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>的战功常冠诸军。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项梁</span>到了<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">薛</span>，听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈王</span>确定已死，就<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚怀王</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项梁</span>号称<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">武信君</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">英布</span>被封为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">当阳君</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项梁</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">定陶</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">败</span>死，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">怀王</span>迁都到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">彭城</span>，各<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸将</span>和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">英布</span>都聚守在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">彭城</span>。当时，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军急<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">围</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>多次派人求<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">救</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">怀王</span>任命<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">宋义</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">上将</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">范曾</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">末将</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项籍</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">次将</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">英在</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒲将军</span>都任将军，全部归属<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">宋义</span>，北上<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">救</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>。等到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项籍</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河上</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">杀</span>了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">宋义</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">怀王</span>便<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">籍</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">上将军</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸将</span>都归属<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项籍</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项籍</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>先<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">渡</span>河<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>屡屡得利，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">籍</span>便全军<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">引兵</span>涉河跟进，于是<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">降</span>伏<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">章邯</span>等。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>军常胜，战功冠于<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>之兵都臣服归属<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，是因<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>常以少<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">败</span>众。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "封九江王",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项籍</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">引兵</span>西进到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">新安</span>，又派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>等夜<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">阬</span>埋<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">章邯</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军士卒<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二十馀万人</span>。抵达关口，不得而入，又派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>等先从小路<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">破</span>关下守军，才得以进入，抵达<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">咸阳</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>常任军锋。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项王</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">封</span>诸将时，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">九江王</span>，建都在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">六</span>。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "英布叛楚",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">汉元年四月</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>都从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">戏下</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">罢</span>兵，各自归国。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项</span>氏<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">怀王</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">义帝</span>，迁都<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长沙</span>，暗中命令<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">九江王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>等人沿途<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span>杀。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">八月</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>派将领<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">义帝</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">追杀</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">郴县</span>。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "称病不佐楚",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">汉二年</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">齐王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田荣</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">畔</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项王</span>前往<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，向<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">九江</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">徵兵</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">九江王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>称病不去，只派部将率<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数千人</span>前往。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>军在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">彭城</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">败</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>又称病不辅佐<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项王</span>因此怨恨<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>，多次派使者责备并召唤<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>愈发恐惧，不敢前往。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项王</span>这时正北忧<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，西患<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>，能倚重的只有<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">九江王</span>，又看重<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>的才能，想要亲近任用他，所以尚未<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span>他。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "随何说淮南",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">汉三年</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，大<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">战</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">彭城</span>，不利，退出<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">梁地</span>，到了<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">虞</span>，对左右说：\"像这些人，不值得与他们商议<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>大事。\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">谒者</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">随何</span>上前说：\"不知<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>指的是谁？\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>说：\"谁能替我出使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">淮南</span>，使其<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">发兵</span>背<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项王</span>拖在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>地<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">数月（时长）</span>，我取<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>便可万全了。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">随何</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>愿出使。\"于是带<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二十人</span>同行，出使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">淮南</span>。到了那里，住在<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太宰</span>府中，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三日（时长）</span>没能见王。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">随何</span>便对<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太宰</span>说：\"王不见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">何</span>，必定是以为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>强而<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>弱，这正是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>此行的缘由。如使<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">何</span>得以进见，所说的话中听，就是大王所愿听的；所说的话不中听，使<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">何</span>等<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二十人</span>伏<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">斧质</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮南</span>市，来向<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">明王</span>表明背<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>而亲<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>也可。\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太宰</span>便转告大王，大王召见了他。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">随何</span>说：\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>派<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>恭敬地呈书于大王御前，不明白大王为什么亲近<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">淮南王</span>说：\"寡人向北以<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>礼事奉他。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">随何</span>说：\"大王和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项王</span>同列为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，却向北以<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>礼事奉他，必是以为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>强大，可以托国。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项王</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>时，身负<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">板筑</span>，为士卒作先锋，大王理当率<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">淮南</span>全部兵众亲自统领，作<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>军前锋，如今却只<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">发</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四千人</span>助<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。向北以<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>礼事奉人，难道就这样吗？<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">彭城</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">战</span>时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项王</span>尚未出<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，大王理当骚动<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">淮南</span>之兵<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">渡</span>淮，日夜到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">彭城</span>城下<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">会战</span>，大王拥<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万人</span>之众，却无<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">一人</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">渡</span>淮的，只是袖手旁观谁胜。托国于人，难道就这样吗？大王凭空名倾向<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，却想厚以自托，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>私下以为不<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">取</span>。然而大王不背<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，是因以<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>为弱。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>兵虽强，但<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>给它加上不义之名，因为它背弃盟约而<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">义帝</span>。然而<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楚王</span>仗着<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">战</span>胜自以为强，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">收</span>纳<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，还守<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">成皋</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">下</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蜀</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汉</span>之粟，深沟高垒，分兵把守要塞，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>兵<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">还兵</span>，中间隔着<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">梁地</span>，深入敌国<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">八九百里</span>，欲<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">战</span>则不能，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻</span>城则力不足，老弱运粮于<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千里</span>之外；<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>兵到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">成皋</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>军坚守不动，进不得<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻</span>，退不得脱。所以说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>兵不足依仗。假使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">胜</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>必自危相<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">救</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>之强，适足以招致<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>之兵罢了。所以<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>不如<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>，其势易见。如今大王不依附万全之<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>，反托身于危亡之<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>私下为大王疑惑。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>并非说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">淮南</span>之兵足以<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">亡</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。大王<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">发</span>兵背<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项王</span>必被拖住；拖住<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">数月（时长）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>取<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>便可万全。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>请与大王提<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">剑</span>归<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>必<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">裂地</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">封</span>大王，更何况<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">淮南</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">淮南</span>必定为大王所有。所以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>特派使者<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>下呈愚计，愿大王留意。\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">淮南王</span>说：\"请奉命。\"暗中答应<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">畔</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>归<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>，未敢泄露。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "杀使叛楚",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>使者正在，急迫催<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">英布</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">发</span>兵，住在客舍里。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">随何</span>径直进入，坐在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>使者的上座，说：\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">九江王</span>已经归<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>凭什么能<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">发</span>兵？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>愕然。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>使者起身。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">何</span>便劝<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>说：\"事已成局，可立即<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">杀</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>使者，不要让他回去，然后迅速奔<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>并力。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>说：\"就照使者所教，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">起兵</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>吧。\"于是<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">杀</span>使者，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">起兵</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项声</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">龙且</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">淮南</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项王</span>留军<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">下邑</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">数月（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">龙且</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">淮南</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">破</span>了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>军。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>想<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">引兵</span>奔<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>，恐怕<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楚王</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">杀</span>他，便从小路与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">何</span>一同归<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "归汉封王",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">淮南王</span>到时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉高祖\">上（汉高祖）</span>正踞坐在床上洗脚，召<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>进见，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>大怒，后悔前来，想<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">自杀</span>。出来到客舍，帐幕、用具、饮食及随从官员都跟<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>的一样，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>又大喜过望。于是派人进入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">九江</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>军已派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项伯</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">收</span>编<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">九江</span>的兵力，把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妻子</span>全部<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">杀</span>光。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>的使者得到一些故友及<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">幸臣</span>，率领<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数千人</span>归<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>军又分配兵力给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>，一同北上，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">收兵</span>到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">成皋</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四年七月</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">淮南王</span>，一同<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项籍</span>。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "破楚垓下",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">汉五年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>派人进入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">九江</span>，攻得数县。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">六年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刘贾</span>进入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">九江</span>，诱降<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大司马</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周殷</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周殷</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">反</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，于是<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">举</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">九江</span>兵与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">垓下</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">破</span>之。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "随何之功",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项籍</span>死，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>平定，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉高祖\">上（汉高祖）</span>设酒宴。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉高祖\">上（汉高祖）</span>贬低<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">随何</span>的功劳，称<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">何</span>为腐儒，说治<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>哪用得着腐儒。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">随何</span>跪着说：\"当<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">引兵</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">彭城</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楚王</span>还没有离开<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>时，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">发</span>步卒<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五万人</span>，骑兵<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五千</span>，能以此<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">取</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">淮南</span>吗？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉高祖\">上（汉高祖）</span>说：\"不能。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">随何</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">何</span>与<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二十人</span>出使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">淮南</span>，到了那里，就如<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>所愿，这是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">何</span>之功胜过步卒<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五万人骑</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五千</span>。然而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">何</span>是腐儒，说治<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>哪用得着腐儒，为什么？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉高祖\">上（汉高祖）</span>说：\"我正在考虑<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>的功劳。\"于是任<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">随何</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">护军中尉</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>于是<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">剖符</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">淮南王</span>，建都<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">六</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">九江</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">庐江</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">衡山</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">豫章</span>郡都归属<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>。"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "入朝汉廷",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">七年</span>，朝见于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陈</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">八年</span>，朝见于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雒阳</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">九年</span>，朝见于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长安</span>。"
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "见醢恐惧",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十一年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高后</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">诛</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">淮阴侯</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>因此心生恐惧。夏天，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">诛</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">梁王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭越</span>，把他<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">醢</span>成肉酱，盛着肉酱遍赐<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>。送到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">淮南</span>时，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">淮南王</span>正在打猎，看见肉酱，大为恐惧，暗中命人部署<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">聚兵</span>，派人窥伺邻郡的警急。"
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "贲赫告变",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>所宠爱的姬妾生病，请求就医，医家与<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中大夫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">贲赫</span>对门，姬妾多次到医家，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">贲赫</span>自以为是<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">侍中</span>，于是厚厚馈赠，跟随姬妾在医家饮宴。姬妾侍候王时，从容谈话间称赞<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赫</span>是长者。王发怒说：\"你从哪里知道的？\"便具说原委。王怀疑她有私情。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赫</span>恐惧，称病。王更怒，想<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">捕</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赫</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赫</span>便上书言变事，乘驿车奔<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长安</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>派人<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">追</span>，没追上。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赫</span>到了，上告<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉高祖\">上（汉高祖）</span>变事，说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>谋<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">反</span>有迹象，可先发制人<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">诛</span>他。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉高祖\">上（汉高祖）</span>读了他的奏书，告诉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">萧</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>不应该这样，恐怕是仇怨者妄诬。请把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赫</span>囚起来，派人暗中查验<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">淮南王</span>。\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">淮南王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赫</span>因罪逃亡，上告<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉高祖\">上（汉高祖）</span>变事，本已怀疑他说出国中隐秘；<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>使者又来，颇有些验查，于是<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">族</span>灭<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赫</span>家，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">发兵</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">反</span>。<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">反</span>叛消息传来，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉高祖\">上（汉高祖）</span>才<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">赦</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">贲赫</span>，任命为将军。"
    },
    "15": {
      "title": "薛公论三策",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉高祖\">上（汉高祖）</span>召诸将询问：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">反</span>了，怎么办？\"诸将都说：\"<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">发兵</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span>他，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">阬</span>这<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">竖子</span>罢了。他能做什么！\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汝阴侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">滕公</span>召来原<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">令尹</span>询问。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">令尹</span>说：\"他本当<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">反</span>。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">滕公</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉高祖\">上（汉高祖）</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">裂地</span>封他为王，疏爵使他尊贵，南面为<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万乘</span>之主，他<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">反</span>是为什么？\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">令尹</span>说：\"往年<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭越</span>，前年<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩信</span>，这<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三人</span>同功一体。他自疑祸及于身，所以<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">反</span>。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">滕公</span>把这话转告<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉高祖\">上（汉高祖）</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>的门客原<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">令尹</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">薛公</span>，此人有筹谋之计，可以问他。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉高祖\">上（汉高祖）</span>便召见询问<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">薛公</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">薛公</span>回答说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">反</span>不足怪。假使<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>用上策，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">山东</span>便非<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>所有；用中策，胜<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">败</span>未可知；用下策，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>可安枕而卧。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉高祖\">上（汉高祖）</span>问：\"何谓上策？\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">令尹</span>答：\"东<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">取</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>，西<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">取</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">并</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">取</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>，传檄<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，固守其地，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">山东</span>便非<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>所有。\"\"何谓中策？\"\"东<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">取</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>，西<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">取</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">并</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">取</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>，据<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">敖庾</span>的粮仓，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">塞</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">成皋</span>之口，胜<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">败</span>未可知。\"\"何谓下策？\"\"东<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">取</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>，西<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">取</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">下蔡</span>，辎重归于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>，自身归<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长沙</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>可安枕而卧，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>无事。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉高祖\">上（汉高祖）</span>问：\"他会用哪一策？\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">令尹</span>答：\"用下策。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉高祖\">上（汉高祖）</span>说：\"为什么舍上中策而出下策？\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">令尹</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>原本是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">丽山</span>刑徒，自己挣到<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万乘</span>之主的位子，此皆为自身谋，不顾身后替<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>万世着想，所以说会出下策。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉高祖\">上（汉高祖）</span>说：\"好。\"<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">薛公</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千户</span>。于是<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">立</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">长</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">淮南王</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉高祖\">上（汉高祖）</span>便<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">发兵</span>亲自东<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>。"
    },
    "16": {
      "title": "黥布兵起",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>初<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">反</span>时，对他的将领说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉高祖\">上（汉高祖）</span>老了，厌倦用兵，必定不会亲来。派<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸将</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸将</span>里只怕<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">淮阴</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭越</span>，如今都已死，其余人不足畏惧。\"于是便<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">反</span>。果如<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">薛公</span>所料，东<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">荆</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">荆王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刘贾</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">走</span>死于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">富陵</span>。尽数<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">劫</span>夺其兵，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">渡</span>淮<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">发兵</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">徐</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">僮</span>之间与之<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">战</span>，分为<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">三军</span>，想以相互<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">救</span>援为奇策。有人劝<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>将说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>善于用兵，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>素来畏惧他。且依<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">兵法</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>在自己地上<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">战</span>为散地。如今分为三军，他<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">败</span>我一军，其余都会逃走，怎么能相<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">救</span>！\"将领不听。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>果然<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">破</span>其一军，其余<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">二军</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">散</span>逃。"
    },
    "17": {
      "title": "兵败身死",
      "text": "于是西进，与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉高祖\">上（汉高祖）</span>的军队在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蕲</span>西相<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">遇</span>，会战于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">甀</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>兵极精锐，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉高祖\">上（汉高祖）</span>便在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">庸城</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">壁</span>垒据守，遥望<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>军的阵法如<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项籍</span>军，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉高祖\">上（汉高祖）</span>厌恶。与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>遥遥相望时，远远对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>说：\"何苦要<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">反</span>？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>说：\"想做皇帝罢了。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉高祖\">上（汉高祖）</span>怒骂他，随即大<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">战</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>军<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">败</span>走，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">渡</span>淮，数次停下<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">战</span>，不利，与<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百馀人</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">走</span>至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">江南</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>原与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">番君</span>联姻，所以<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长沙</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">哀王</span>派人<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">绐</span>骗<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>，假说一同逃亡，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">诱</span>引去<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>信之并跟随到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">番阳</span>。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">番阳</span>人在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">兹乡</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>家田舍中<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">杀</span>了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>，于是<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">灭</span>了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黥布</span>。"
    },
    "18": {
      "title": "封立后事",
      "text": "<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">立</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">长</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">淮南王</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">贲赫</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">期思侯</span>，诸将大多以功受<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">封</span>。"
    },
    "19": {
      "title": "太史公论英布",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">英布</span>，他的先祖难道就是<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">春秋</span>所载的被<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">灭</span>的<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">英</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">六</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">皋陶</span>的后代吗？自身遭受<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">刑法</span>，崛起为何如此迅猛！<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项</span>氏<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">阬杀</span>人以<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千万数</span>，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>常为元凶。功冠<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，因此得以封王，却也不免自身成为世上大<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">僇</span>戮的对象。祸端起自宠姬，妒忌生患，竟以<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">灭</span>国！"
    },
    "20": {
      "title": "赞",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">九江</span>初次占卜，当刑而称王。 免刑于徒众之中，聚众为盗于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">江</span>上。 两次称雄<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>军，频频<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>将。 因病为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：项羽\">羽（项羽）</span>猜疑，归附而受<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>之杖责。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">贲赫</span>被毁谤，终致无妄之祸。"
    }
  }
}